title: The Signs as Villanelle Quotes
body:
Aries: "I think about you, too. I mean I masturbate about you a lot."
Taurus: "I like buying things. I like owning them. I like looking at them. All kinds of things."
Gemini: "This is so boring!"
Cancer: "Who's your favorite? Me or her? It's me, huh, a little bit?"
Leo: "Why did they want me in there? I am amazing."
Virgo: "I'm just looking out for you, Eve."
Libra: "I won't need money. Aaron wants to buy everything for me. Maybe we're soulmates."
Scorpio: "Will you give me everything I want?"
Sagittarius: "Yes, I am funny."
Capricorn: "Most of the time, most days, I feel nothing."
Aquarius: "Normal is boring. I'm not normal, you know."
Pisces: "I really liked you."
